Q1. Design Java application using JDBC for the following use Exception wherever necessary[25 Marks]
Consider a table with following format--- contains multiple records
Serverid, Server location, duration, purchase date, validity end date, Ram, price
123, Dubai, 4 days,2018-12-12,2019-12-12, 50GB, 500000.00
Create serverPOJO ,serverDao & Tester for the following requirements.
Display following menu
1. Add new server ---- Add new server in the existing file
2. Delete a server ---- Delete server from file
3. Search servers based on no of days ---accept no of days from user display all servers with duration <
or equal to given duration
4. Search servers based on price----accept price from user display all servers with price < or equal to
given duration
5. Exit